# School Timetable Assignment (2024/2025)

This project is a **school timetable** built using **HTML and CSS**.  
It covers classes for **Years 7–9, Monday to Friday**, with proper structure, styling, and accessibility features.

---

## 📂 Project Structure

---

## 🛠 Features
- Timetable built with `<table>` elements.  
- Proper use of **rowspan** and **colspan** where needed.  
- Clear background colours for **Break** and **Clubs**.  
- Consistent structure across all 5 days.  
- Accessible table with headings and semantic markup.

---

## 🔍 Accessibility Notes
- Table headers (`<th>`) are used for **days** and **time slots**.  
- Break and Clubs are visually distinct with background colours.  
- Font is easy to read with good contrast.

---

