## ✅ Validation
Before submitting:
1. Check HTML at [W3C HTML Validator](https://validator.w3.org/).  
2. Check CSS at [W3C CSS Validator](https://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/).  
3. Fix any errors if found.

---

## 📤 Submission
- Zip the folder `Kapedo_Mrussian` (with all files inside).  
- Upload the `.zip` file in the assignment submission portal.  
- Alternatively, share the GitHub repository link.

